    <item>
      <title>美国药店销售好于预期，沃尔格林股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/walgreens-posts-stronger-than-expected-revenue-at-us-pharmacies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃博联公司 (Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc.) 公布的季度销售额超出了华尔街的预期，推动其股价创下 45 年来的最大涨幅，并缓解了该连锁药店在考虑包括出售在内的战略选择时所面临的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/walgreens-posts-stronger-than-expected-revenue-at-us-pharmacies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
